<i>noun</i>: 고전주의 [고ː전주의/고ː전주이] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>고전주의 [고ː전주의/고ː전주이]</dt><br>
<dd>classicism</dd><br>
<dd>17~18세기 유럽에서 형식을 중요하게 생각했던 예술의 흐름.</dd><br>
<dd>A style of art putting emphasis on form, which appeared in Europe during the 17th and 18th centuries.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>